data.description: HOME FOR THE HOLIDAYS! PRICED TO SELL! This fabulous stand alone home offers the privacy of a single-family home with the amenities of townhome living! Feel like you are at the top of the world, nestled in the treetops! The mid-century modern esthetic compliments the open floor plan features soaring wood-beamed vaulted ceilings and a gorgeous, stacked stone fireplace with wood mantel. The home chef will love the modern kitchen with stylish two-toned cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and sleek quartz countertops. Preparing culinary delights is a breeze! Unwind at the end of the day in the primary oasis including a luxurious ensuite with a large vanity, step-in shower with glass enclosure and a walk-in closet. Well-appointed secondary bedroom and adjacent updated full bath. There’s even a bonus space--ideal for a nursery, office or even a third bedroom. Got pets? Enjoy the convenience of the portable dog run right off the deck! Right down the street from Paso Nodal Dog Park and great hiking trails! Two-car garage. Pool and clubhouse. Conveniently located on the 12th hole in tranquil Golf Ridge in Pleasant Hill near highly-rated Mt. Diablo schools including Valhalla Elementary, shopping, transportation, parks, hiking, and the best of the East Bay. Welcome home!
